    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款AI驱动的太空跑商游戏，穿梭于150+颗星球，600+智能NPC的真实动态宇宙。你可以从一名新手商人起步，经营店铺、打造商会，最终成为联结各方势力的大老板，影响整个星系的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的经济系统由AI驱动，供需与价格并非固定数值，而是通过 NPC 的立场、关系与选择共同塑造。跑商不只是赚钱，也是在参与并改变文明的运行规则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/e0a5b457c9cf4583bd056f1e69e02575.webp?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/36c4344868699801ecb4a36f89e1648c.poster.avif?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/36c4344868699801ecb4a36f89e1648c.webm?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/36c4344868699801ecb4a36f89e1648c.mp4?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>多重命运与无限沙盒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>告别线性流程，体验多种截然不同的人生轨迹：</strong>你可以扮演新手商人，通过物品的低买高卖跑商赚钱；也可以扮演商会经理，打通商路和管理员工；或者选择做一个大老板，结盟军事势力。当然，你也可以选择做一个自由者，在AI驱动的动态世界里，书写自己的荧河传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/ce505f2bc0bfcc1d47418638c2ad9c4c.poster.avif?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/ce505f2bc0bfcc1d47418638c2ad9c4c.webm?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/ce505f2bc0bfcc1d47418638c2ad9c4c.mp4?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>AI 驱动的动态NPC世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的每一次选择都会真实影响这个世界：</strong>游戏中 600+ 名 NPC 由 AI 驱动，拥有独立的身份背景、长期目标与行动逻辑。他们会根据你的行为、市场变化与阵营关系持续做出选择，而这些决策将真实影响贸易环境、势力结构与世界走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/bc07d95e21fdd050420084d1e65a1668.poster.avif?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/bc07d95e21fdd050420084d1e65a1668.webm?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/bc07d95e21fdd050420084d1e65a1668.mp4?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>AI 驱动的动态NPC世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的每一次选择都会真实影响这个世界：</strong>游戏中 600+ 名 NPC 由 AI 驱动，拥有独立的身份背景、长期目标与行动逻辑。他们会根据你的行为、市场变化与阵营关系持续做出选择，而这些决策将真实影响贸易环境、势力结构与世界走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/a58640e91a5ee173e486041268c54870.poster.avif?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/a58640e91a5ee173e486041268c54870.webm?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/a58640e91a5ee173e486041268c54870.mp4?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>模拟经营 × Roguelike</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法融合带来独特的游戏体验：</strong>一个看重资源积累，一个强调死亡重来，融合在一起会带来什么样的游戏体验？在这里你需要从零建立开拓站，在有限资源与时间压力下调配人口、改造设施并解锁科技路线。随机事件、周期性磁暴与未知危机接连出现，你需要不断修正计划，寻找生存与扩张的最优解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/6b5d7ffa993b696325e683a25b72e1a4.poster.avif?t=1772191877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/6b5d7ffa993b696325e683a25b72e1a4.webm?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/6b5d7ffa993b696325e683a25b72e1a4.mp4?t=1772191877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>探索未知，重建文明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索扩张并塑造星际版图：</strong>在广袤星图中航行，探索遗迹、触发随机遭遇战，寻找失落的科技。从一名匆匆过客，逐步进化为这片星空的统治者，你的荧河故事由你自己来书写。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105960/extras/147780b3a828c3cc703c99a78ed5ede6.avif?t=1772191877\" width=800 height=477 /></span></p>",
